window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Liam wasn't supposed to be my happily ever after. He wasn't even on my radar. He was my husband's best friend - forbidden. </p> <p>But my husband is dead, and I'm alone. I ache for him, and I reach for Liam. </p> <p>One night with Liam changed everything. Now I have to decide if I truly love him or if he's just the consolation prize. </p>"; 
